data.description: Take a look at this spacious 3 bedroom 2 bathroom 2187SF home conveniently located on the west side of Dothan. It is on a corner lot in the Fox Hollow Subdivision off of Flowers Chapel Rd. which is convenient to several restaurants, shops, and Flowers Hospital. Enjoy a screened in porch as well as a beautiful light and airy sunroom that is currently used as a play room and an extra entertainment area. The home offers an open floor plan with large family room with vaulted ceiling and a fireplace. There is extra storage in the attached two car garage as well as two storage buildings in the back yard that will stay.
